Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you like Brussels sprouts? Some people do, and some people don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.14,0:00:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you roll your tongue?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.14,0:00:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Again, some people can and some people can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.51,0:00:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though we're all members of the same species, <i>Homo sapiens</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.51,0:00:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,we're all different to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.24,0:00:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Even offspring of the same parents are genetically different
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.24,0:00:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and genetic variation is fundamental to life and the way that life evolves.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.95,0:00:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Our genetic code is carried by this molecule.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.87,0:00:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This is DNA
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.12,0:00:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,or deoxyribonucleic acid
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.14,0:00:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and variation is introduced into this molecule in a number of different ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.63,0:00:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,In sexually reproducing animals, like us
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.80,0:00:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,we create variety by making sex cells, eggs and sperm
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.68,0:00:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,with unique combinations of genes from each parent.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.00,0:00:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But there can also be mutations. This means changes to the units
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.93,0:01:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,the nucleotides that make up the DNA.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.48,0:01:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This can happen because of copying errors,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.23,0:01:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,or because of damage to the DNA.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.66,0:01:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Mutations sound like bad news
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.88,0:01:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,but in fact they're crucial to creating variety
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.20,0:01:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and without them evolution would virtually grind to a halt.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.44,0:01:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's evolution that has created the diversity of life on the planet
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.72,0:01:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and allowed life to evolve and adapt to changing environments.
